Fan Control Module (FCM) Fan_CPLD   I2C_12 0x70: 
Channel2 (0x02) accesses 0x51 FCB Inv (24C02);
Channel5 (0x10) accesses 0x52 FAN#1 (24C64);
Channel6 (0x20) accesses 0x52 FAN#2 (24C64);
Channel7 (0x40) accesses 0x52 FAN#3 (24C64);
Channel8 (0x80) accesses 0x52 FAN#4 (24C64);

PWR_CPLD's 0x23 register (TIMER_MISC)
bit0 (POWER_CYCLE_GO) is used to initiate the power cycle. Write 1 to start the cycle;
bit1 (TIMER_COUNTER_SETTING_UPDATE) is used to update timer parameters.
